text: WDEL may refer to: * WDEL (AM), a radio station (1150 AM) licensed to serve Wilmington, Delaware, United States * WDEL-FM, a radio station (101.7 FM) licensed to serve Canton, New Jersey, United States * WVUE (Delaware), a defunct television station (channel 12) formerly licensed to serve Wilmington, Delaware, which held the call sign WDEL-TV from 1949 to 1955
title: WDEL
